    "Details": "The 55 variant of the Jackal is a modification that is built to enhance its long range accuracy. This was done by removing the anti-missile system and replacing it with an advanced targeting computer, which allowed the Jackal to attack an enemy with even greater long-range accuracy in a sniper role. The long requested switch from standard to double heat sinks enhances the design yet further, and allowed dropping one heat sink to boost armor.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Cooling Jacket - PPC</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.99</color></b>",
